components.templateData:
<mat-form-field appearance="outline">
  <input
    matInput
    [placeholder]="label"
    [value]="defaultValue"
    [required]="required"
    [min]="min"
    [max]="max"
  />

  <mat-icon matIconPrefix *ngIf="matIconPrefix">{{ prefixIcon }}</mat-icon>
  <mat-icon matIconSuffix *ngIf="matIconSuffix">{{ suffixIcon }}</mat-icon>

  <mat-hint>{{ hints }}</mat-hint>
</mat-form-field>
